title: 183: What is Our Relationship w/ Gross Foods? | Ear Biscuits Ep. 183
description:
Bugs, blood, and the world's spiciest pepper. You may have seen them eat it all, but how were they actually feeling in the process? R&L reveal it all and how their culinary exploits on Good Mythical Morning may have changed their views on food forever on this episode of Ear Biscuits.
